            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間17日10:01，深證成指下跌261.54點（或2%），暫報12824.87點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-4.66%</li><li>近 1 月：+0.17%</li><li>近 3 月：+22.07%</li><li>近 6 月：+33.88%</li><li>今年以來：+29.72%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>培育鑽石概念領跌-2.87%。其中    四方達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300179:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300179\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300179-CN</a>)            下跌        6.68%            ;        楚江新材(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002171:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002171\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002171-CN</a>)            下跌        6.13%            ;        晶盛機電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300316:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300316\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300316-CN</a>)            下跌        5.05%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>虛擬電廠概念領跌-2.70%。其中    中恆電氣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002364:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002364\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002364-CN</a>)            下跌        9.05%            ;        科陸電子(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002121:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\"